description: Korea's famous street cuisine is making its way to you, thanks to Sun Kim Bop! Staying true to the spirit of Korean street food, the Bop Burger, Spicy Pork Wrap, and more, are the perfect foods to eat on the go. Chef Sun took her nostalgia for the food of her homeland to the streets of Massachusetts, and she's made an amazing menu that is sure to make your everyday lunch into an astounding experience!
name: Sun Kim Bop
